WELCOME
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Ushahidi Java ME client allows a user to post to and view reports from an Ushahidi deployment.


System Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- A CDC/CDLC Java enabled cellphone.
- Adequate RMS storage.


Online Resources
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
A list of resources you might need is given below. Feel free to fork the repository, sort issues and/or add missing features.

*About Ushahidi - http://www.ushahidi.com 
*Application design - http://prezi.com/rwmt6imyacr7/ushahidi-java-me-app/
*Application Program Interface(API) - http://wiki.ushahidi.com/doku.php?id=ushahidi_api
*Java ME source - github.com/ushahidi/Ushahidi_j2me

For further references and documentation, head over to our wiki (http://wiki.ushahidi.com/doku.php?id=ushahidi_api). You are encourage to drop by our forums (http://forums.ushahidi.com/) if you have any additional questions or concerns.
